WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
[Music]

00:00:04.620 --> 00:00:09.840
Artificial intelligence is fundamentally changing every field,
and these are the people who want to lead that charge.

00:00:10.480 --> 00:00:15.960
This is the AI Incubator, a community of students, faculty,
and staff from all across campus.

00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:22.480
We meet once a week to share strategies, pitch ambitious ideas,
test new tools, and solve real problems with AI.

00:00:23.300 --> 00:00:27.740
These students are founding their own startups,
leading national discussions, and taking on

00:00:27.740 --> 00:00:33.340
real-life projects, like using drones to fly life-saving blood products
to trauma victims in remote areas,

00:00:33.340 --> 00:00:38.640
and building software to help them raise money
for survivors of domestic abuse,

00:00:38.640 --> 00:00:43.900
and putting AI-powered fundoscopic cameras all across rural Kentucky
to catch diabetic retinopathy.

00:00:44.740 --> 00:00:50.260
This is what learning with AI looks like now:
people in a room, building the future together.

00:00:51.140 --> 00:00:51.800
So come join us.

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:53.940
No AI or coding experience is required.

00:00:54.460 --> 00:00:56.600
Just bring your own curiosity,
and we'll see you there.
